    <item>
      <title>以色列誓言回应伊朗袭击，欧洲天然气价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/european-gas-jumps-as-israel-vows-response-to-iran-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列高级军事官员重申，以色列别无选择，只能回应伊朗周末的无人机和导弹袭击，欧洲天然气价格周二持续上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/european-gas-jumps-as-israel-vows-response-to-iran-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 07:05:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗表示，头寸紧张将推动美股回调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/citi-says-stretched-positioning-set-to-fuel-us-stock-pullback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团策略师表示，随着投资者抛售大量期货多头头寸，美国股市的进一步疲软可能会加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/citi-says-stretched-positioning-set-to-fuel-us-stock-pullback</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 06:58:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储重新定价使亚洲股市面临的风险高于其他股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/stocks-look-more-vulnerable-in-asia-than-peers-on-fed-re-pricing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二亚洲股市的大幅抛售凸显了人们对该地区在利率上升和地缘政治紧张局势加剧的情况下脆弱性的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/stocks-look-more-vulnerable-in-asia-than-peers-on-fed-re-pricing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 05:41:28 GMT</pubDate>
