    <item>
      <title>农历新年推动中国航空旅行再创新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-air-travel-hits-fresh-record-on-post-covid-new-year-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于政府努力提振国家旅游业以及国内度假需求强劲，中国航空公司第一季度的载客量创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-air-travel-hits-fresh-record-on-post-covid-new-year-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 04:49:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国小盘股因市场监管收紧而进一步下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-s-small-cap-gauge-tumbles-on-tighter-listing-rules-pledge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于内阁承诺加强市场监管，引发了人们对财务状况不佳的公司退市的担忧，周二中国小盘股的抛售潮延续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-s-small-cap-gauge-tumbles-on-tighter-listing-rules-pledge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 02:23:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在人民币的帮助下，美元在亚洲外汇市场中一路飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/emerging-market-fx-index-drops-to-2024-low-after-iran-s-attack-on-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，美元的复苏大幅削弱了全球货币，使许多货币贬值至受到密切关注的水平，迫使一些官员介入以遏制损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/emerging-market-fx-index-drops-to-2024-low-after-iran-s-attack-on-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 01:25:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中东紧张局势加剧，股票抛售蔓延：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市暴跌，此前亚洲和华尔街因美国利率上升的担忧而引发抛售，而中国经济动力减弱的迹象以及中东紧张局势加剧则加剧了这一情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 22:18:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟被“玩弄”后对中国发起贸易攻势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/eu-goes-on-china-trade-offensive-after-getting-played-for-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟委员会主席乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩正在对中国实施一系列贸易限制，她试图兑现让欧盟在全球舞台上成为更重要的政治参与者的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/eu-goes-on-china-trade-offensive-after-getting-played-for-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:47:02 GMT</pubDate>
